name: Endings (Wherbe)
description:
Endings

The timer counts down, and it seems like there isn't much to do. But maybe there is?

(Note: The endings in this game might be really hard to figure out, I'm not sure since I never had it playtested. Click here for a guide in case you get stuck/frustrated.)
